column3: Central England Temperature (CET) Minimum seasonal temperatures ranked from warmest to coldest
Met Office Central England Temperature dataset
Met Office Central England Temperature dataset
Data represents the ranking of the CET seasonal mean temperatures by season from warmest year to coldest year
The ranking of warmest years on record is also included in the annual columns at the end of the file
missing values are identified with the missing data flag
